ed from the given name in the Middle Ages."]},{"name":"Jerrard","meanings":["Rare variant spelling of   Gerard  , probably influenced by the form of the modern surname, if not a transferred use."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Girard de Rion was born in 1150, in Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France, his father, Falcon II De Réon, was 31 and his mother, Béatrix de Auxonne, was 25. He married De Macon in 1174, in Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1187, in his hometown, at the age of 37."},"et":{"1150–1187":"1150–1187","1155–Female":"1155–Surnud","1175–1221":"1175–1221","1120–Male":"1120–Surnud","1125–Female":"1125–Surnud","1125":"1125","2 de janeiro de 1175":"2. jaanuar 1175","1221":"1221","1155":"1155","1187":"1187","1120":"1120","1175":"1175","1174":"1174","1150":"1150","Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, França":"Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa","Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France":"Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Prantsusmaa","Gergy, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne-Franche-Comté, France":"Gergy, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne-Franche-Comté, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1150–1187":"1150–1187","1155–Female":"1155–Kuollut","1175–1221":"1175–1221","1120–Male":"1120–Kuollut","1125–Female":"1125–Kuollut","1125":"1125","2 de janeiro de 1175":"2. tammikuuta 1175","1221":"1221","1155":"1155","1187":"1187","1120":"1120","1175":"1175","1174":"1174","1150":"1150","Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, França":"Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Ranska","Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, France":"Créon, Gironde, Nouvelle-Aquitaine, Ranska","Gergy, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne-Franche-Comté, France":"Gergy, Saône-et-Loire, Bourgogne-Franche-Comté, Ranska"},"fr":{"1150–1187":"1150–1187","1155–Female":"1155–Décédée","1175–1221":"1175–1221","1120–Male":"1120–Décédé","1125–Female":"1125–Décédée","1125":"1125","2 de janeiro de 1175":"2 janvier 1175","1221":"1221","1155":"1155","1187":"1187","1120":"1120","117